Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.24,Insert-Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an3\pos(1840,312)}生意気ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.53,Insert-English,,0,0,0,,{\pos(45,105)\fad(150,150)}Do I seem cold?{Do you see me as blunt/cold?}
